perl-Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer
-------------------------------------------
podviewer provides a simple and attractive way to read Perl's POD
documentation. You can use it to read the Perl POD pages, module 
documentation, and information about Perl's builtin functions.

Runtime requirements:
  perl-5.8.8-4
  perl-Glib-1.144-1
  perl-Gtk2-1.146-1
  perl-IO-stringy-2.110-1
  perl-Locale-gettext-1.05-1
  perl-Pod-Simple-3.05-1

Build requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.24-2
  cygport-0.3.5-1
  make-3.81-1
  perl-5.8.8-4

Canonical homepage:
  http://search.cpan.org/~gbrown/Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer/

Canonical download:
  http://www.cpan.org/authors/id/G/GB/GBROWN/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack perl-Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer-0.17-1-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./perl-Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer-0.17-1.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/perl-Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer-0.17-1-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/perl-Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer-0.17-1.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /etc/postinstall/perl-Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer.sh
  /usr/bin/podviewer
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/Gtk2/Ex/PodViewer.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/Gtk2/Ex/PodViewer/Parser.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.8/cygwin/auto/Gtk2/Ex/PodViewer/.packlist
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/perl-Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer-0.17.README
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer-0.17/README
  /usr/share/man/man1/podviewer.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man3/Gtk2.Ex.PodViewer.3pm.gz
  /usr/share/man/man3/Gtk2.Ex.PodViewer.Parser.3pm.gz
  /usr/share/perl/cygwin-pods/5.8/Gtk2-Ex-PodViewer.pod

